Brent Corrigan is an all American football hero who secretly yearns for another man's touch, so smooth daddy Adam Russo gives the frustrated stud what he needs. Uptight, geeky actor Josh Pierce gets a royal opening from hot, hung muscleman Trenton Ducati, and arrogant musician Cliff Jensen gives in to beautiful Brandon Wilde.
